description:
&lt;p&gt;Loo&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;king for a new challenge? Then join our team!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a great chance for a highly motivated Registered Anaesthetic Nurse/O.D.P. to develop their career with one of Europe’s largest heart and lung centers. Although we work primarily on adult and paediatric cardiothoracic patients we also cover all specialties with underlying cardiothoracic conditions.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will you be broadening and deepening your anaesthetic experience in a partnership of two specialist hospitals which are known throughout the world for their expertise, standard of care and research success, using the latest technology and pioneering new techniques, working in our department of 6 operating theatres including a new £7,000,000 state of the art hybrid theatre, 4 catheter laboratories and in ancillary areas covering MRI and CT imaging work. You will also benefit from superb training and development opportunities and in a fabulous location within the heart of Chelsea.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; We need an enthusiastic practitioner to join our Anaesthetic Team at the Royal Brompton Hospital. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Cardiothoracic experience would be beneficial but is not essential as training will be given on commencement of the post.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be expected to complete our competencies within an agreed period of time, dependent on your experience, before commencing on-call duties.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;In return you can expect a departmental orientation program, along with support to undertake Theatre Courses and opportunities to participate in our monthly Academic program. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We encourage all our staff to achieve a healthy work/life balance in a friendly, supportive environment where people are keen to share their skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
